<div class="main large"><h3>Toggle Buttons</h3>
  <p>Toggle buttons can be created by using a button-group and the class <i>toggle</i>.</p>
<code><pre>
&lt;div class="btn-group toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
  &lt;a class="btn toggle-blue active hover">&lt;/i>Girl&lt;/a>
  &lt;a class="btn toggle-blue">&lt;/i>Boy&lt;/a>
&lt;/div>
</pre></code>

