<div class="main large"><h3>Button Groups</h3>
  <p>
    Use the class <i>btn-group</i> for button groups.<br>
    Use the <i>data-toggle="buttons"</i> attribute to enable radio button like behaviour.<br>
    Use the <i>data-toggle="button"</i> attribute to enable checkbox like behaviour.
  </p>
  <br><br>

<code><pre>
&lt;div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons"&gt;
  &lt;a class="btn gray"&gt;Button One&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class="btn gray"&gt;Button Two&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class="btn gray"&gt;Button Three&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre></code>
  <br><br>

  <h6>With <i>data-toggle="buttons"</i> attribute</h6>
  <br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons">
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 1</a>
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 2</a>
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 3</a>
  </div><br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons">
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 1</a>
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 2</a>
  </div><br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons">
    <a class="btn gray">Choice 1</a>
  </div>
  <br><br>

  <h6>With <i>data-toggle="button"</i> attribute</h6>
  <br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="button">
    <a class="btn gray">1</a>
    <a class="btn gray">2</a>
    <a class="btn gray">3</a>
  </div><br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="button">
    <a class="btn gray">1</a>
    <a class="btn gray">2</a>
  </div><br>
  <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="button">
    <a class="btn gray">1</a>
  </div>
</div></div>